        <% if (!isAuthenticated) { %>
            <div class="jumbotron index-page">
                <div class="container">
                    <h1 id="happytag">WELCOME TO HAPPINESS</h1>
                    <p id="front-quote">"Pushing For Cloud 9"</p>
                    <div class="card">
                        <p>This app is to help survivors of Sexual Assault, PTSD, Trauma, or other anxiety to help you reach and Stay at Cloud 9. We can do this. You can do this. Stay positive and motivated. I hope this app helps you in some way. --Maddie
                            Glance
                        </p>
                    </div><br>
                </div>
                <a href="https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/therapists" target="_blank"><button class="btn btn-danger get-help">Get
        Help</button></a>
            </div>
            <div class="about-author container">
                <div class="image-cropper">
                    <img class="profile-image" src="/images/w.jpg" alt="Author">
                </div>
                <div class="author-text">
                    <p>C9ForLife was created by Maddie Glance a Survivor. See her story at www.c9forlife.com. She is on a journey to help other survivors come forward, help people with PTSD, and to fix the justice system in hopes to make a safer world for
                        all those who are survivors of trauma. Remember that you are not alone, there are many others who are here to help you. Together we can get through the anxiety, fear, and move forward to acheive your own Cloud Nine.

                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% } else if (isAuthenticated) { %>
